text: This obsoletes IRM 4.19.24 Compliance Identity Theft.

It is now obsolete. The material relating to Compliance Identity Theft previously contained in IRM 4.19.24 is incorporated into new IRM 25.23, Identity Protection and Victim Assistance, and IRM 4.19.13.25, Campus Exam Identity Theft. This was with the consolidation of identity work in Management.
IRM 4.19.24, Compliance Identity Theft, is obsolete as of the date of this transmittal..
This transmittal is intended for SB/SE (Small Business/Self-employed) and W&I (Wage and Investment) Examination Operations.
